text: Nice neighbourhood park with butterflies to watch. There is information board about the garden attracting butterflies. And a compass state built there to represent compass-vale.
Peaceful environment with a young population. Love that Sengkang MRT and CompassOne Mall are within walking distance.
I live here. Dusty because we are near the main highway but amenities and transport options are bundant here
Easy to access Compass One, waterway point and the nearby Sengkang Hospital is going to be ready soon.

It's my house! It's PERFECT!
Compass One to the left, and Waterway Point to the right. What's not to love? :)
